</h1><p><a href="https://matrix.to/#/@bilelmoussaoui:gnome.org">Bilal Elmoussaoui</a> says</p>
<blockquote>
<p>During Google Summer of Code, Dave Patrick worked on rewriting <a href="https://flathub.org/apps/org.freedesktop.Bustle">Bustle</a>.
The work consisted of:</p>
<ul>
<li>Switching from Haskell to Rust</li>
<li>Port to GTK 4</li>
<li>Modernize the UI &amp; codebase</li>
</ul>
<p>You can read about the GSoC progress at <a href="https://seadve.github.io/tags/gsoc-2023/">https://seadve.github.io/tags/gsoc-2023/</a> and the release is available on Flathub!

